Ly do tai sao cac website 18+ van hoat dong den hien nay:

1. Nhu cau cao tu nguoi dung: Internet co hang ty nguoi su dung, va mot phan lon quan tam den noi dung nguoi lon.

2. Mo hinh kinh doanh loi nhuan: Cac trang web nay kiem tien qua quang cao, dang ky thanh vien, ban noi dung, va cac dich vu khac.

3. Khung phap ly khac nhau: Nhieu quoc gia cho phep hoat dong voi quy dinh (nhu tuoi toi thieu 18), khong cam hoan toan.

4. Kho kiem soat tren internet: Mang luoi toan cau, vo danh, va cong nghe lam cho viec chan toan bo rat kho.

5. Tu do ngon luan va quyen rieng tu: Nhieu cuoc tranh luan ve quyen truy cap thong tin cua nguoi lon.

6. Tien bo cong nghe: De dang xay dung va host website, su dung VPN, proxy, va cac cong nghe an danh.

7. Kinh te: Tao viec lam va dong gop vao nen kinh te so o mot so noi.